criteria.textblock:
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  women;

          -  over 65 years old;

          -  with OAB with or without UI;

          -  able to walk without mobility aid; consent to participate in the study

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  neurologic pathology; history of spine surgery;

          -  cognitive impairment defined as a MMSE < 24;

          -  legal protection
